<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 06:14:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>菲律宾特使表示，特朗普担任总统期间印太立场没有变化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/no-change-indo-pacific-stance-under-trump-presidency-says-philippine-envoy-2024-02-28/</link><description>菲律宾长期驻华盛顿大使周三表示，如果唐纳德·特朗普在总统竞选中获胜，美国的印太战略不太可能改变。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 06:10:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/no-change-indo-pacific-stance-under-trump-presidency-says-philippine-envoy-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>由于对自由的担忧，香港准备制定更严格的安全法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-moves-towards-enacting-tougher-security-law-amid-concerns-about-2024-02-28/</link><description>香港新国家安全法的公众咨询期于周三结束，人们担心当局希望尽快实施的这项立法将进一步侵蚀这个金融中心的自由。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 05:48:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-moves-towards-enacting-tougher-security-law-amid-concerns-about-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>需求预期看跌挑战铁矿石价格弹性</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/bearish-demand-expectations-challenge-iron-ores-price-resilience-2024-02-28/</link><description>尽管中国经济前景黯淡，但铁矿石价格长期保持坚挺，但自农历新年假期结束以来，铁矿石价格大幅下跌，引发了人们对需求疲软的担忧，并削弱了澳大利亚主要生产国的矿业股。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 05:12:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/bearish-demand-expectations-challenge-iron-ores-price-resilience-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>碧桂园：债务问题有多严重？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-how-bad-are-its-debt-problems-2024-02-28/</link><description>中国开发商碧桂园周三表示，因未支付 2.05 亿美元贷款而收到清算申请，这给其债务重组前景蒙上阴影，并削弱了北京方面恢复房地产行业信心的努力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 05:06:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/country-garden-how-bad-are-its-debt-problems-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>图瓦卢新政府重申与台湾的关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-tuvalu-government-reaffirms-relationship-with-taiwan-2024-02-28/</link><description>图瓦卢政府在一份声明中表示，图瓦卢新政府在上个月的选举后重申了与台湾的关系，并补充说它希望与澳大利亚就去年签署的安全协议进行对话。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:51:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-tuvalu-government-reaffirms-relationship-with-taiwan-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国鼎晖投资正在洽谈收购价值 17 亿美元的越南杂货连锁店的少数股权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-cdh-talks-buy-minority-stake-17-bln-vietnam-grocery-chain-say-sources-2024-02-28/</link><description>两名知情人士称，中国鼎晖投资公司正在就从越南零售商 Mobile World 手中收购 Bach Hoa Xanh (BHX) 少数股权进行深入谈判，这笔交易可能使这家杂货连锁店的估值高达 17 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:41:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-cdh-talks-buy-minority-stake-17-bln-vietnam-grocery-chain-say-sources-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>丰田1月份全球产量增长7%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyotas-global-output-rises-by-7-january-2024-02-28/</link><description>日本丰田汽车周三表示，受益于美国强劲的需求，1 月份全球汽车产量增长 7%，连续第 13 个月同比增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:36:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyotas-global-output-rises-by-7-january-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，随着中海油退出，嘉能可关注壳牌新加坡资产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/glencore-eyes-shell-singapore-assets-cnooc-pulls-out-sources-say-2024-02-28/</link><description>几位行业和贸易消息人士称，瑞士矿业和大宗商品贸易商嘉能可(Glencore)正在考虑收购壳牌在新加坡的炼油厂和石化部门，该石油巨头在先前的收购者退出后正在寻找买家。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:27:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/glencore-eyes-shell-singapore-assets-cnooc-pulls-out-sources-say-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国扩大国家秘密法，将“工作秘密”纳入其中</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-broadens-law-state-secrets-include-work-secrets-2024-02-28/</link><description>据官方媒体报道，中国立法者自 2010 年以来首次扩大了北京的《国家秘密法》，根据网上发布的该法全文，将受限制的敏感信息范围扩大到“工作秘密”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:13:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-broadens-law-state-secrets-include-work-secrets-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>韩国和美国将举行年度演习，重点关注朝鲜核威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-us-stage-annual-drills-focusing-korea-nuclear-threats-2024-02-28/</link><description>官员周三表示，韩国和美国将于下周开始年度春季军事演习，重点是阻止朝鲜使用核武器的可能性。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 04:03:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-us-stage-annual-drills-focusing-korea-nuclear-threats-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国称其海警在台湾岛屿周围巡逻“无可非议”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-its-coast-guard-patrols-around-taiwan-islands-beyond-reproach-2024-02-28/</link><description>中国政府周三表示，中国海警在中国海岸附近的台湾岛屿周围的巡逻“无可非议”，并驳回了有关台湾游船登船引发恐慌的抱怨。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 03:21:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-its-coast-guard-patrols-around-taiwan-islands-beyond-reproach-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国通胀测试即将到来，亚洲股市走势缓慢；猕猴桃幻灯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-28/</link><description>周三，亚洲股市在美国本周公布的通胀数据之前表现谨慎，这可能会影响美联储宽松周期的时机，而在央行软化利率鹰派立场后，新西兰元大幅下跌。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 02:33:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国称北京和莫斯科应加强亚太协调</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-beijing-moscow-should-strengthen-coordination-asia-pacific-2024-02-28/</link><description>中国外交部周三表示，中俄应加强在亚太事务中的沟通协调，共同维护地区安全、稳定和发展。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 02:15:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-beijing-moscow-should-strengthen-coordination-asia-pacific-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾总统称中国海军在南海的存在“令人担忧”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-navys-presence-south-china-sea-is-worrisome-says-philippine-president-2024-02-28/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周三表示，中国海军在南海的存在“令人担忧”，但不会阻止菲律宾保卫其海洋领土和保护其渔民。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 00:48:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-navys-presence-south-china-sea-is-worrisome-says-philippine-president-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>碧桂园清算申请加剧中国房地产困境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-country-garden-faces-winding-up-petition-failure-pay-2045-mln-loan-2024-02-28/</link><description>中国开发商碧桂园周三表示，因未支付 2.05 亿美元贷款而收到清算申请，这给其债务重组前景蒙上阴影，并削弱了北京方面恢复房地产行业信心的努力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 00:47:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-country-garden-faces-winding-up-petition-failure-pay-2045-mln-loan-2024-02-28/</guid></item></channel></rss>